<i>Ten seconds to the start</i>
<i>of the Belgian Grand Prix.</i>

01:37:24.667 --> 01:37:26.225
<i>Sarti's in the lead at La Source.</i>

01:37:26.402 --> 01:37:29.803
<i>Almost the end of the first lap, and already</i>
<i>he's ahead of the second car.</i>

01:37:29.972 --> 01:37:31.633
<i>It's Pete Aron's Yamura.</i>

